            <title>[SYNAPSE-910] NHTTP transport does not allow to write empty string as a SOAPAction header. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-910</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
